<h2>POST /:user_id/profiles/:folder_id/from/:document_id</h2>

<p>
Creates a profiles folder in the specified user account 
and creates a profile item based on each document item (the text of which we sometimes refer to as 
a "document") from the specified document folder.
Returns a representation of the created profiles folder with a 201 Created HTTP status code.
</p>
<p>
A profile item is formed by analysing the relative frequencies of terms in the document item's text 
as compared to their frequency across the entire document. 
SubSift calculates the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tfâ€“idf" class="external">tf-idf</a> score for each term 
in each document item (document) and also constructs a summary of term statistics for the entire document.
</p>

